sql: SELECT COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.END_TIME , COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.FRIDAY , COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.MONDAY , COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SATURDAY , COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SECTION_NUMBER , COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.START_TIME , COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SUNDAY , COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.THURSDAY , COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.TUESDAY , COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.WEDNESDAY , COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER , SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER , SEMESTERalias0.YEAR FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 , SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 482 AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "FA" AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;
